FBIS4-33085 "drlat106_a_94014" FBIS-LAT-94-106 Daily Report 1 Jun 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Havana Manufactured Gas Service Breaks Down Havana Manufactured Gas Service Breaks Down FL0106221594 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1951 GMT 1 Jun 94 FL0106221594 Havana Radio Reloj Network Spanish BFN [Text] The Manufactured Gas Enterprise of Havana announces to the population that due to mechanical problems at the Evelio Rodriguez Curbelo plant, gas service to every municipality in Havana has been affected. The note adds that work is being done to reestablish this vital service in the next few hours, and apologies are extended to the population for the inconvenience this situation might cause.
